result.title: Bring elegant, 2 bedrooms, Sagrada Familia ,AC
result.description:
Two-bedroom, one-bathroom apartment ideal for a four-person group. One of the bedrooms has a double bed. In the other there are two single beds. The apartment has a spacious living room and a lovely terrace. The kitchen is fully equipped. The bathroom has a modern shower stall. There is also a rooftop terrace with sun-loungers, tables and chairs for all guests, to enjoy a delightful view of Barcelona.
The space
This two-bedroom, one-bathroom apartment is ideal for a four-person group. One of the bedrooms has a double bed. In the other there are two single beds. The apartment has a spacious living room and a lovely terrace. The kitchen is fully equipped. The bathroom has a modern shower stall. Fresh bed linen and towels are provided.

This pretty apartment located in the Eixample, near many famous modernista (Catalan Art Nouveau) buildings and close to Gaudí's famous Sagrada Familia church. There is free Wi-Fi, TV, and air conditioning. Enjoy your stay at Sagrada Familia Apartments, the best place to relax and explore Barcelona. 

NOTE: we have several apartments with the same characteristics, but with different layouts and decoration. In the photos you can see the differences.
Guest access

result.title: Ud -Ma31 Suite with terrace (1 Br )3A
result.description:
THIS APARTMENT IS AVAILABLE ONLY FOR MID TERM RENTALS FROM A MINIMUM STAY OF 1 MONTH (min. 32 days). .
New lovely suite with 1 Double Bed, living area with private balcony and decorated with amazing style.
Located in the center of the Rambla of Poblenou and just few steps away from the beaches and Barcelona's historical district.
The building has been reformed on winter 2016, with modern design and with all needed amenities and features: TV Sat, Free Wifi, Washer/dryer, AiCo/Heater, Coffee machine, Dish Washer, Hair Dryer, Owen MRW, Alarm, Towels Heater, Kettle and Nespresso Coffee machine, Bath amenities.
PROPERTY CONFIGURATION:
The suite comes with:
1 double bed,
1 living area with double sofa bed (suggested for 1 adult or 2 kids)
1 bathroom with shower, towels heater, bidet and all the amenities
1 terrace with outdoor table for dinner
1 fully equipped kitchen with all utensils
OPTIONAL SERVICES available on request:
Airport transfer, VIP Airport Transfer, Grocery Shopping, Daily cleaning, City Tours, Concierge services.
TRAVELLING DURING COVID19
1- SANIFICATION: In Urban District Apartments we extremely care about the safety & security of our dear Guests and Personnel. To do so, we have implemented a strict Covid-19 Prevention Protocol based on international recommendations, so to host you in an confortable and safe apartment. All surfaces, towels, bedlinen, bath amenities and kitchens equipments have been property sanitised and handled with disposal gloves. All our personnel has been trained according to the COVID19 Sanification Standards and continuously monitored.
2- VIRTUAL CHECKIN: You can have free access to the apartment just using your smartphone without keys handover and personal interactions with the Reception personnel. Do the online checkin before arrival and get your Access Code to access the property. You will not need to handle physical key.
3- PROTECT YOU AND THE OTHERS: Urban District Apartments will provide as courtesy, an Hand Sanitiser Gel, so to protect you and the others. Prevention suggestions will be available at the property.
4- SUPPORT and ASSISTANCE: In case of need of support our Reception Office and Service Team will be available to assist you on site or by phone.
LOCATION:
Poblenou is the trendiest area in Barcelona.
Famous for its strategic location just between the old historical district and the beaches. Poblenou keep the essence of its traditions and authentic quality of life.
The famous Rambla of Poblenou with the restaurants, bars, the grocery markets and the art galleries make it as the ideal district for your holidays away from crowdy touristic areas.
The beaches and the beach clubs are an amazing place to relax with family and friends.

result.title: Mango Sun
result.location: Rda. de Atocha, Madrid, Lavapiés , Spain
result.description:
If you're craving culture, look no further than this artfully positioned pad in Atocha. You'll find it nestled in Madrid's Golden Triangle of Art, boasting proximity to the Prado and Thyssen Museums – a fifteen-minute walk away – and offering a front-row seat to the striking red facade of the Reina Sofia Museum. Here, you're in a prime spot for exploring, with El Retiro Park and the Plaza Mayor just shy of twenty minutes away on foot.

Inside, white walls and heaps of natural light create an inviting canvas primed for relaxation. We especially love the open-plan living space. Vibrantly furnished and adorned with an eclectic array of artwork, it beckons you to unwind between adventures, curled up in the cosy lounge or roosted at the dining table with a glass of wine. Though, the real highlight is the balcony. After a restful slumber, step outside through the large glass doors to sip your morning coffee in the sunshine.

result.title: South Faling Townhouse-LA Cerquilla Nueva Andalucía Golf Valley
result.description:
GOLF VALLEY- €2,000 m2, South facing four bedroom townhouse situated in the heart of the golf valley in Nueva Andalucia, surrounded by the international Golf courses of Las Brisas, Aloha and Los Naranjos. A wide range of amenities as supermarkets, international schools and banks can be easily reached within a short drive away.

The fully gated complex, built in 2003, consists of 52 multi coloured houses offering a large swimming pool with waterfall, two putting greens, changing room, CCTV system and exceptionally kept gardens. The property, divided in three levels plus basement, comprises on the recepeption level Entrance hall, living/dining area with fireplace and access to a covered terrace, kitchen, guest bedroom with access to the terrace and guest toilet.

On the upper level, there is the master bedroom with en-suite bathroom boasting a private solarium with sea views. In the basement, there are two further guest bedrooms -one of which converted in to a large walk-in wardrobe- guest bathroom, storeroom and private garage for one car.
result.location_address: Urbanizacion N Andalucia 2G, 54B, 29660 Marbella, Málaga, Spain

result.title: Timeless Designed Villa Located in La Cerquilla Nueva Andalucía
result.description: Nestled high above the Mediterranean Sea lies this villa – a timeless retreat inspired by traditional Ibizan architecture. Located in the prestigious community of La Cerquilla in Nueva Andalucia, with stunning views to several golf courses, La Concha and the sea. The most exclusive neighbourhood in Nueva Andalucia, with spectacular properties all set in a gated community and close to all amenities, Puerto Banus with its 24/7 lifestyle including luxury boutiques, restaurants, nightlife, proximity to the beach and to Marbella. With over 1.000m2 of built, set on a plot that measures 3.000m2, the villa will boast amenities that cannot be found anywhere else in Marbella. New owners can enjoy an indoor pool with both steam and infrared sauna as well as a jacuzzi, cold pod, gym, bodega, screening room, game room, massage room, relaxation room and a glam-room which includes a hairdresser and make-up station. The main level offers 6 bedrooms and 7 baths, a large gourmet kitchen, dining room, TV room and a spacious living room overlooking the immaculate garden. The beautiful manicured grounds showcase a spacious patio with infinity pool, floating seating group and pool house. Although the property provides unique entertainment areas for residents, guests, kids and families alike, it still provides a deep feeling of relaxation within its own peaceful refuge, a contrast to the world outside, with design and surroundings that provide calm and harmony. This property is a millennium of art, architecture and engineering under one roof. An extremely rare property that must be experienced!
result.location_address: Urbanizacion N Andalucia 2G, 54B, 29660 Marbella, Málaga, Spain

result.title: Alona Golf Front Line Refarbished Ground Floor Apartment with Sublime Views

As you walk in, the first thing that will amaze you is the stunning views over the ocean. In the livingroom and terrace/garden, there is also excellent view over the iconic "La Concha"-mountain. Very bright home with Scandinavian design, sold fully furnished.

The apartment is currently used for rentals, which it is great for.

result.title: Oustaning Beachfront Penthouse in Torre Bermeja
result.description:
This modern stylish property comprises three large bedrooms and bathrooms, spacious open plan interior and fully fitted kitchen equipped with the latest appliances. Some of the highlights of the penthouse are Bang & Olufsen music system, TV and DVD pre-installation, Wi-Fi, Satellite TV and under floor heating. Bathrooms also benefit from hydro-massage baths, steam and sauna showers, double glazing and an alarm.

Torre Bermeja is positioned on the New Golden, with easy access to Puerto Banús and the surrounding coastal towns. The luxury beachfront development is set within stunning gardens featuring sub-tropical plants, water features and swimming pools. The Andalucian style properties provide stylish interiors finished to the highest specifications and are positioned to provide uninterrupted views of the Sierra Bermeja mountain range.

A wide range of on-site facilities are available for residents’ enjoyment, including two wellness centres, fitness club, spa, gym and three communal swimming pools. There are also 24 hour security surveillance and monitored intruder alarms. The local vicinity includes 30,000m2 of protected land, two 5-star hotels, Laguna Village, the famous Tikitano Beach Restaurant and a tennis club.

result.title: La Cerquilla Cutting Edge Designed Modern Villa
result.description:

Nestled in the heart of the Golf Valley, this luxurious home is located within a short distance to all amenities of Nueva Andalucía and the exclusive golf courses. This bespoke home has been finished to the highest quality standards, offering top quality materials throughout.

Distributed over three levels, it welcomes you into an impressive entrance hall with double height ceiling, which leads to a large open-plan living area. The large living room is furnished with high quality furniture and overlooks the tropical garden of the villa. The living room connects with the impressive dining area and the modern kitchen.

The living room and dining area have direct access to the covered and uncovered terraces, with several chill-out areas and stunning infinity pool. Upstairs, the villa welcomes you into spacious bedrooms, overlooking the greens of Los Naranjos Golf. The lower level boasts an extra large entertainment area with TV room and possibility to customize with more features. It is truly one of the most exceptional homes in Nueva Andalucía as per its fantastic elevated plot, high qualities, cutting-edge architecture and prime location.

result.title: Brand New Model Front line Golf Villa
result.description:
Just finished! Superior finishing qualities, contemporary design villa, project of the prestigious architecture studio GonzálezandJacobson, South-West orientation first line golf, located in La Cala Golf Resort, with three 18-hole golf courses. Five minutes from one of the best beaches on the Costa del Sol with its typical Chiringuitos bordering the Sendero del Litoral, in the middle of an idyllic landscape, bordering 7 km of sea between the rocks to Puerto Cabopino in Marbella.

The location enjoys an extreme tranquility.Description: Entering through a large portal with remote control is a garage with capacity for 5 cars, spacious and bright connected to the side of the machine room (pool cleaner, heat pump for the underfloor heating throughout the villa, 2 tanks of water reserve and site for tools), on the other a large surface for laundry and another that could be used as a leisure place, a cinema or even an office with the possibility of installing a large window.A wide central staircase with space for a possible hydraulic glazed elevator(optional), communicates to the next floor and entrance/reception, being left a good surface for the kitchen in an open plan, annexing the living and dining room, bordered by an exceptional pool and leisure and comfort area for "alfresco" meals under a design pergola. The access to the terrace and garden areas is through two huge windows that reach from the floor to the ceiling. Towards the right side of the entrance to the villa there is a complete bathroom and an office or bedroom for guests that focus on the pool on one side and a covered porch and garden with views over the lake at Hole6 of the golf course by the other. On the upper floor, there are three additional bedrooms; one of them is the master bedroom with bathroom on suite a large terrace with excellent views and a spectacular dressing room.

Another bathroom is located next to the other 2 bedrooms. All bedrooms have large windows with magnificent views. Round out these exquisite villa extras such as: air conditioning, alarm, heated floor in bathrooms and underfloor heating throughout the villa, automatic sprinkler irrigation, fitted wardrobes in all bedrooms, pre-installation of solar panels, lighted garden, as well as the swimming pool. With the purchase of this villa La Cala Golf Resort offers a Privilege card with discounts at the Hotel, bar/restaurants and for the owners and family to be a member with an annual, very special fee, of the three golf courses.

result.title: Beachfront  Showstopper Estate in the New Golden Mile

The property finds itself within a tranquil, exclusive residential area that is close to all amenities, including golf, fine dining and shopping, but offers a unique blend of seaside location and peace. La Perla Blanca offers direct access to a sandy beach along its 60 metre-wide sea-fronting plot, as well as uninterrupted views of the sea all the way to Gibraltar and North Africa.

result.title: A Stunning Well designed and presented detached Villa  in Rio Real Marbella
result.description:
A stunning, well designed and presented detached villa in Rio Real, Marbella.

The villa is located in the quiet urbanization Lomas del Pozuelo in the Rio Real area, near to elegant ‘beach clubs’ and one of the best golf courses on the Costa del Sol. five minutes drive from the city or the beach and 35 minutes from the airport.

Situated in an elevated position in relation to the rest of the neighborhood with a beautiful, landscaped garden to the front as well as a driveway for parking. The villa was built with green energy in mind and is super efficient thanks to a solar panel and storage battery installation.

The accommodation is over three levels, with the living, dining and open plan kitchen on the ground floor, the living room has a full wall of windows that open out onto a large terrace with barbecue area, another delightful feature is the central fireplace which gives an ambient glow to both the living and dining areas.

The first floor provides a master suite with super-sized walk in dressing room as well as an en-suite bathroom, the room leads out onto a terrace where we can enjoy panoramic views of the sea and La Concha. There are two further guest bedrooms on this level that share a family bathroom.

The large swimming pool tiles are special pool tiles from Spanish company (Serena mix), this tiles give not only the pool but also the whole garden a very exclusive look, the looks you expect of a villa in this price category. The swimming pool has also a shower area.

The German kitchen is equipped with a Smeg oven and Smeg American fridge/freezer, dishwasher of Siemens which is connected through app for control. The kitchen has a (nature stone) black granite counter top with extra bar area for 2 bar chairs. All Smeg appliances are black and harmonize with the black counter top and the white kitchen. Integrated Led Lighting strip with controller above counter top for ambiance lighting.

The basement has an 100m2 total, where a laundry area is created and the technical room, the area could be further developed into a games or cinema
room or an additional bedroom if required.

All in all, this is a sensibly priced villa in an attractive location with a traditional layout, super energy efficient and with easy access to amenities, our personal opinion is that this is a great value villa, stunningly and meticulously presented throughout.

result.title: EI Paraiso Corner unit - Newly Reformed Duplex Apartment with Stunning views
result.description:
Semi Detached Ground floor Duplex apartment in El Paraiso with newly reformed 2 Bathrooms with windows and natural light (Upstairs a spacious wet room), fully air conditioned apartment making ideal for rentals or a home, the master bedroom boasts its own private terrace and private views over the mediterranean.

A Divine south facing apartment which delights in both panoramic mountain and sea views, well priced for an apartment with this potential.

Lovely gardens with looking over the tropical gardens and pool to the sea. With only 20 apartments in the community ensuring peace and serenity throughout the year.

On the main floor, this south facing apartment offers a wide entrance hall, recently renovated bathroom with window, a bedroom with direct access to the main terrace, enjoying mature garden and sea views, modern open fitted kitchen, bright living and dining room with a new fireplace, the living space opens to a wide uncovered terrace with a private access to the community swimming pool and tropical garden.

Located in a heart of El Paraiso in small, charming and quiet community, enjoying exclusive golf courses and the beach on your doorstep (only a few minutes drive), bars, restaurant and Chiringuitos all nearby.

Double glazing, A/C hot and cold, Security, Parking space and large storage room included.

result.title: Stylish Contemporary Penthouse with Sea Views
result.description: Brand new, modern penthouse on the beachside of San Pedro de Alcantara. A truly special property, with a southern orientation, gorgeous sea views and a sleek clean design. Within 5 minutes walk to the town centre, shops restaurants, amenities, and some 200m away from the beach, location is perfect. The penthouse has a jacuzzi, 3 parking spaces and a storage room.
result.location_address: Av. de Santander, 29670 Marbella, Málaga, Spain

result.title: Newly Renovated Spacious Ground Floor Apartment
result.description:
This newly renovated 4 bedroom ground floor apartment is lcoated in the urbanization of El Dorado in Nueva Andalucia, a prime location in the heart of the golf valley. It´s bright and spacious property comprising an entrace hall, two living rooms, fully equipped kitchen with direct access to the covered terrace.

The accommodation consists of 3 double en suite bedrooms and one single room, guest toilet inthe entrace hall. Direct access to the pool, disigner kitchen with central island, are features that makes this property desirable. Close to the main golf courses in the area, walking distance to amenities and a short drive to Puerto Banus.

result.title: New Golden Mile Front ilne Beah Renovated
result.description:
Fully renovated top quality 4-bedroom ground floor apartment in Bahia del Velerin. Frontline beach, soutH facing, sea views, quiet and private. Direct access to the beach.

Spacious living and dining area with fully fitted open plan kitchen (Neff appliances). Master bedroom and guest bedroom en suite and two guest bedrooms sharing a bathroom.
Underground parking and storage.

Direct access from the living areas to a large terrace and the communal nature and lush gardens and community pool.

Great location, next to the famous chiringuito El Velerin and walking distance to Laguna Village. Less then 5 minutes drive to all amenities.

result.title: Spectacular Modern villa close to Golf courses
result.description:
Spectacular villa nestled in the heart of El Herrojo’s, this contemporary 6 bedroom villa is surrounded by numerous golf courses, with panoramic views to Marbella’s coastline and within the immediate vicinity of Nueva Andalucía and Puerto Banús.

Exquisitely designed in a modern style, this 3 level estate is a paradise for family and friends and open to the light and the views only Southern Spain can offer.
Built throughout three levels, the main floor comprises an expansive open plan area, complete with a stylish living and dining area with a beautiful custom designed bodega and an enormous fully fitted kitchen, which all lead effortlessly to the tropical outdoors. Exterior areas include luscious tropical gardens with a private swimming pool, outdoor kitchen and lounge areas, providing an oasis feeling.

This quality modern home features 6 bedrooms, plus an extra space which has currently been converted into an office. The lower floor is dedicated to entertainment and relaxation including a play room, cinema room, gym and a garage that fits up to 4 cars.
result.location_address: C. Pánfilo de Narváez, 29678, Málaga, Spain

result.title: Casasol Turnkey Villa
result.description:
new turnkey project in urb. Casasola, next to Guadalmina Baja on a spacious plot of 3.842m2. This home has a distinct, elegant appearance and will be completely refurbished inside and out in order to create a brand new home in a traditional property.

The new house will be built to the highest standards. Spacious and bright with pure elegance in a perfect blend of natural materials and elements.

The house offers a large living area with an open plan fully fitted kitchen, 5 to 6 bedrooms, direct access to the big garden and pool area.

Situated in a residential area with lush surroundings and walking distance to the beach. Close to all amenities.

It is possible to built a 2nd villa with a separate entrance.
result.location_address: C. de la Grulla, 44b, 29688 Atalaya Isdabe, Málaga, Spain

result.title: Sierra Blanca- Luxury villa with stunning Gradens
result.description:
Villarroel designed villa with a €1.25 million renovation, including the development of the lower level to include an unbeatable private cinema and bar with 9 Italian leather recliner armchairs, private spa, and gym.

The interior decoration of this house is extremely high including Italian silk curtains throughout and the very best furniture materials. Inside, on the ground floor the property offers a large lounge with triple height ceiling opening onto the covered main terrace, garden and pool with sea view, a grand dining room with vaulted ceiling and candelabra feature, 2 fully equipped kitchen areas including chef/party catering and breakfast area, 2 guest bathrooms, and three en-suite double bedrooms with dressing areas, as well as the impressive entrance hall and staircase with interior palm trees.

Upstairs the huge master bedroom suite offers a very large bathroom with top-spec therapeutic Jacuzzi bath, large walk-in shower, mezzanine office area overlooking the lounge, large dressing area, and a private terrace with stunning panoramic sea views.

The lower level includes a 3 car garage with individual electric doors and easy road access, private spa with extra large Jacuzzi tub and Sauna, gym and large state-of-the-art cinema and bar, and another double bedroom suite. The easy to maintain garden is very private and offers a large heated swimming pool in a beautiful mature setting. All in all, this very stylish property offers first-class luxury qualities in Marbella´s most sought-after Golden Mile address. Sold fully furnished.

result.title: Sierra Blanca Immacalate Modern style semi-Detached Houses
result.description:
This luxurious, super stylish house for sale in Sierra Blanca, one of the most sought-after areas in the whole Mediterranean region, offers the best qualities and extraordinary
features. Surrounded by the beautiful nature and similar high-end properties of the upper Golden Mile, it exposes the modern Mediterranean style where contemporary architecture is enriched by unique avant-garde features and Scandinavian hygge. Settled in a privileged elevated position, the south-oriented property enjoys incredible sea and mountain panoramic views.

Built to the highest standards, the impressive house of 679 m2 has 3 floors connected with a lift and an ultra-modern staircase. It features an entrance hall; spacious open plan living and dining areas; a fully-fitted, black & white sleek kitchen with breakfast area and exit to al fresco dining terrace; 3 cozy bedrooms; 3 superbly equipped bathrooms, etc. One of the wow-factors of this villa is its custom contemporary wine room, bodega. Additionally, it enjoys a great outdoor space on the roof; a top terrace offers a solarium,
BBQ, alfresco dining and relaxing areas, and a Jacuzzi overlooking the magnificent mountain and the sea all the way to the African coastline. The wonderful terraces of 166 m2 are perfect to be experienced in all year-round warm and mild Mediterranean climate. The outdoor private swimming pool invites to immerse in its crystalline water. A garage can hosts 3 cars.

This eco-friendly and energy-efficient property comes for sale in excellent condition, with state-of-the-art technology, sophisticated lighting and ceiling solutions, panoramic glass doors and oversized windows, double glazing, a fireplace and many other luxurious features. It is fully furnished and boasts the chic interior thoroughly created by the famous designer Pedro Peña. Expect top quality and impeccable taste, attention to exquisite detail and one-of-a-kind décor objects! The neutral colour palette invests in elegance and comfort of this outstanding semi-detached villa.

The residents of this exclusive gated development in Sierra Blanca enjoy the high standards of luxury, having their own SPA-center with indoor heated pool and gym, stunning
landscaped gardens and 24h security service.

result.title: Spectacular El Madranal villa with Amazing sea views
result.description: Spectacular house situated in the cozy hillside of El Madroñal. The house benefits from its elevated position and offers amazing sea views. The ground floor comprises of a big hall, two living rooms, a spectacular dining room and a beautiful contemporary kitchen. On the lower level, there are three good sized bedrooms, a gym, laundry room and spa. All the bedrooms have beautiful sea views, floor to ceiling windows, direct access to the garden and an en-suite bathroom. The 1. floor consists of a breathtaking master suite, with a big walk-in closet, private 0 m² terrace with amazing views and a lavish 7 master bathroom.

result.title: Villa Chopo
result.location: C.chopo near carr.de benahavis, cortés , Marbella spain
result.description:
Villa Chopo is a spectacular villa in the heart of Paraiso Alto.

Distributed over three levels, the villa comprises, on the entrance level; a large dining room and living room, spacious kitchen featuring a large central island and incorporating a breakfast area benefitting from the natural light of the bay windows and views of the banana trees. The entrance hallway has access to the guest toilet and to the two generous guest bedrooms sharing one bathroom. Terrace access is from the living room and leads down to the pool area beyond.

Upstairs, we find the third large guest bedroom with en-suite bathroom featuring a double basin, a full jacuzzi bath as well as a large standalone walk-in shower. The master bedroom suite is a real highlight , being very generously sized and featuring a walk-in dressing room as well as a very large bathroom with double basin, jacuzzi bath and walk-in shower.

On the lower level is the large double garage along with the laundry room and two storage rooms, with an additional external storage room for garden equipment etc. In addition to the garage, the entrance drive incorporates a turning circle with ample parking space

The interior fittings of the property are of very high quality with air conditioning throughout, underfloor heating, travertine marble in the bathrooms etc.

The property is set on a large 1800m2 plot allowing for ample garden space as well as the large pool and surrounding area.
